quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  31,20,"E on yi'aali, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, wonnde Alla newianii on nafitorgol ko woni ka kammuuli kon, immorde e naange, e lewru e koode, O newinani on kadi ko woni ka leydi kon, immorde e daabeeji, e leЙ—Й—e e puЙ—i. O timminnirani on neemaaji Makko Й“annguЙ—i, wano labeede maa moЖґЖґude mbaadi, e neemaaji suuЙ—iiЙ—i, wano haqqil e ganndal. E hoore ko Й—in neemaaji woodi kon fow, hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, wennjiroowo fii wootinЙ—ingol Alla, ko aldaa e tuuginagol e ganndal wahayu, immorde ka Alla, maa haqqil ndayginorki, wanaa fere Deftere Й“anngunde, jippiniraande ka Alla."
  31,21,"Si Й“ee wennjooЙ“e fii wooЙ—indingol Alla ngol wi'anaama: "Jokkee wahayu mo Alla jippini on e NulaaЙ—o Makko on", Й“e wi'ay: "Men jokkataa Й—um. Wurin ko ko men tawri baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en kon, e rewugol sanamu, men jokka". E hara Й“e jokkay baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, hay si tawii seytaane woniino noddiroowo Й“en e ko rewugol sanamuuji majjinayЙ—i Й“e, Й—i Й—owira e lepte Yiite dulЙ“oowe ngen Г‘alnde Darngal?"
  31,22,"Kala fewtirЙ—o e Alla, o laЙ“Й“inani Mo dewe Й—en, o moЖґЖґini golle makko Й—en, gomЙ—ii haray o jogitike ko Й“uri hoolnaade e ko jortiiЙ—o daЙ—al jogitotoo, tawde o hulaa nde Й—um taЖґata. Awa ko faade ka Alla tun, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in, O yoЙ“ita gooto kala e hanndi."
  31,23,"Kala yedduЙ—o Alla, wata keeferaaku makko sunine suninean NulaaЙ—o. Ko ka Amen tun, woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, Men humpita Й“e ko huuwunoo e bonЙ—i ka aduna, Men yoЙ“ita Й“e Й—um. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e fondooji Й“erЙ—e. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—um."
  31,24,"Men dakmitiray Й“e ko Men okki Й“en kon e dakamme aduna, yeru seeЙ—a tun, refti Men jooГ±iroya Й“e e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e Г‘alnde Darngal, Й—en woni lepte Yiite."
  31,25,"Pellet, si an NulaaЙ—o, a lamndike Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: "Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin?" Ma Й“e wi'u: "Ko Alla tagi Й—i!" Maakan Й“e: "Yettoore woodani Alla feeГ±inЙ—o hujja on e mon!". Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, sabu majjere maЙ“Й“e nden, Й“e anndaa hannduЙ—o e yettoore."
  31,26,"Ko Alla tun woodani tagu, e laamu e toppitagol kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla, ko Kano woni YondiniiЙ—o e tagu Makko ngun fow, YettiniiЙ—o aduna e laakara."
  31,27,"Hay si tawii leЙ—Й—e ko woni ka hoore leydi kon fow, settiraama karambi, maayo ngon waЙ—taa ndaha, ngon Й“eydiraa maaje jeeЙ—iЙ—i, konnguЙ—i Alla Й—in lannataa, tawde wanaa ko lannata. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Mo gooto foolataa, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e tagu Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  31,28,"Tagugol on, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, e immintingol on Г‘alnde Darngal fii hasbeede yoЙ“ee, wonaali, si wanaa wa tagugol fittaandu wooturu, immintinira ndu no newori. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo, Mo nanugol hito goo, haЙ—ataa Mo nanude hito woo. Ko O Yi'oowo, Mo yi'ugol goЙ—Й—um goo, haЙ—ataa Mo yi'ude huunde woo. Ko wano non kadi woniri, tagugol maa immintingol wonkii woo, ronkinirtaa Mo fii wonkii goo."